(secondQuint)Anticholinergic Risk Scale and Resource Use After Elective Noncardiac Surgery.

 Multilevel multivariable regression analysis will be used to investigate the adjusted association between preoperative Anticholinergic Risk Scale and postoperative healthcare resource utilization.

 Sensitivity analyses will be used to evaluate the robustness of the primary analysis.

